Scientific Calculator:

AIM OF THE PROJECT
Aim is to make a simple scientific calculator application for Android and publish it to playstore. 

DETAILS OF THE PROJECT
To make a simple scientific calculator, you will understand the concepts of 
- Basics of UI elements and android Java
- Importance of callback methods
- Understanding of guidelines to follow before publishing app to playstore.

TECHNOLOGY STACK
- Android
- Java
- XML

ROAD MAP
- Basic understanding of app development (Android and XML) - 2 Days
- Implementation with mathematical logic - 2 Days
-  Experimenting with several UI elements to make your app ready for playstore - 1 Day

